Question: Explain how to reach your home without using any street names
Answer:
From this location? Take an illegal right at the red light. At the stop sign turn left. At the red light, turn right. Go through the next two lights and head straight until you come to a bridge on the left. Turn left. Make a right and an immediate left right before the road ends. Go straight. You will hit a speed limit sign for 35 Miles per hour. Take the next right. Take the next right again. Take the second left. It's the first place on the left.